com.jmr.wrapperx.common

Class HttpSession

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jmr.wrapperx.common.HttpSession
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IConnection

    public class HttpSession
extends java.lang.Object
implements IConnection
    Networking Library HttpSession.java Purpose: A client's session connected to a servlet. Used by the server and client. Gives the method needed to send objects over HTTP. Holds cookie information to keep track of clients on the server.
    Version:
    1.0 8/4/2014
    Author:
    Jon R (Baseball435)
